---
title: Tex-Mex Pork & Veggies with Rice, Slaw & Herby Mayo
description: Discover classic Tex-Mex flavours with this aromatic rice bowl, piled with saucy pork, tender veggies and zingy slaw. Top it off with a some herby mayo and you’ve got a dinnertime hit!
